國無可能永遠都強大，以前八十年代夠話日本增長落去，將成世界第一經濟體&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"044336d3c0869a25ccdc927190b307d2e442e56c","tid":351024,"uid":25265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:46:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打仗係連登毒撚翻身好時機</blockquote><br />\n到時野外求生真係係咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef8e8ff5dd40bfe943e57f962244a3bf25999a9","tid":351024,"uid":25265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:46:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔想返工返學囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到時可以日日食樹皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40ca0e04b87c0eb0d46a74daf2a95abe69221b3","tid":351024,"uid":25265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:47:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係人類本身既意識就係咁？ 一去到個循環，好戰既慾望就出哂嚟</blockquote><br />\n講到尾都係錢作怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b895dd3f26cdfbb7eb90a04ff3ebf5b9f09a4207","tid":351024,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:48:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係想打仗，係想中國俾人打姐，呢啲垃圾國家，強大左一定遺禍世界</blockquote><br />\n中國打唔信香港無影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最好殺埋你老母</blockquote><br />\n而家有人話中國畀人打香港會無影響咩？"},{"pid":"cd60e813e1be50edd82d6a606c05e6c1a3f8defb","tid":351024,"uid":25265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:49:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係想打仗，係想中國俾人打姐，呢啲垃圾國家，強大左一定遺禍世界</blockquote><br />\n到時全國宣佈緊急狀態<br />\n香港就好似要行中國法例(好似係，有錯巴絲直接屌)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65ae230cc34ca6631f99d718c2716579d8b68b3","tid":351024,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:49:09.000Z","msg":"冇左核彈的阻嚇<br />\n可能已經打緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f94f98d91918b0cd39c99607ac97bd3fc36af7","tid":351024,"uid":25265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:50:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係想打仗，係想中國俾人打姐，呢啲垃圾國家，強大左一定遺禍世界</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國無可能永遠都強大，以前八十年代夠話日本增長落去，將成世界第一經濟體&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n非也<br />\n中國根本未全面開發<br />\n中國地大人多 好似地區都係平地 無野起<br />\n佢依家仲聲稱自己係發展中國家咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd91eb094f0b6590ca12989a353ec8d781cb75b8","tid":351024,"uid":25265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:51:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇左核彈的阻嚇<br />\n可能已經打緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n核彈得個擺字 根本無咩可能用<br />\n因為大家都知一用就攬炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b99ec5fe981aa796ef33db19aa31c9cd0f9a920","tid":351024,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:53:11.000Z","msg":"連登仔 只係 網上面話想打仗<br />\n如果現實入面真係打仗, 打到來香港<br />\n<br />\n到時 連登仔 就會喊哂口話唔想打仗嫁啦"},{"pid":"86053213a06e60f55f1d552add260a756f4812a2","tid":351024,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:54:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打仗係連登毒撚翻身好時機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連登仔 以為自己係關羽, 張飛<br />\n一旦打仗, 就去前線殺敵, 然後上位 做大將軍<br />\n<br />\n但實際上, 連登仔 只係 揚州十日, 嘉定三屠 既其中一個平民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e62f9d55e9601404cfc5af5263fdfbfc0f17f2e","tid":351024,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:56:22.000Z","msg":"證明全世界用緊既社會生活模式係錯囉。"},{"pid":"60b10f0e7141e08b98ed21c420c0fd5ff545692c","tid":351024,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:56:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係想打仗，係想中國俾人打姐，呢啲垃圾國家，強大左一定遺禍世界</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國無可能永遠都強大，以前八十年代夠話日本增長落去，將成世界第一經濟體&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n非也<br />\n中國根本未全面開發<br />\n中國地大人多 好似地區都係平地 無野起<br />\n佢依家仲聲稱自己係發展中國家咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但首先要換政權先<br />\n<br />\n一日中共執政, 中國都唔洗指意強大<br />\n<br />\n因為中共其實係出賣緊中國既利益, 資源.......令自己發達, 再帶住D錢移民去外國"},{"pid":"6a9870901002e30b8085d8a4667d2aa9e88e3164","tid":351024,"uid":25265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:58:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>證明全世界用緊既社會生活模式係錯囉。</blockquote><br />\n一切都係資本主義既錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32a27a20d685244fcf535a94d84d08be044b645","tid":351024,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:06:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係人類本身既意識就係咁？ 一去到個循環，好戰既慾望就出哂嚟</blockquote><br />\n人類體內一直都存在住戰爭基因同殺戮慾望"},{"pid":"b171f91ab185e0470de68f64c96309fa4671b7d6","tid":351024,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T20:19:27.000Z","msg":"人類不嬲有殺戮慾望<br />\n<br />\n不過想打仗嘅係連登仔同支那憤青啫"}]}